snippet.title: Flying Neko Delivery Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Flying Neko Delivery is a game about a feline witch who lives in the forest and delivers packages. Earn money from each delivery to customize your cottage. Explore new worlds, forage plants and fungi, and befriend villagers along the way! https://store.steampowered.com/app/410740/Flying_Neko_Delivery/ #indiegames #gaming #pcgames
